Function Reference/remove theme mods « WordPress Codex
-----------

Remove all theme modification options for current theme.

Usage
-----

` <?php remove_theme_mods() ?> `

Parameters
----------

None.

Return Values
-------------

 (void) 
:   This function does not return a value.

Examples
--------

Notes
-----

Change Log
----------

Since: 2.1.0

Source File
-----------

`remove_theme_mods()` is located in `wp-includes/theme.php`.

